<blockquote>
<CENTER><img src ="/mrc/images/fedstick.jpg"><br>
<h1><I> MRC Membership Benefits </I></h1></center><BR>
As an MRC Member you'll receive these great benefits.....
<ul>
<li><b>FREE!!!</b>  A 12-month subscription to <a href="/mrc/membership/flash.html"><I>Flash</I></a>, MRC's Monthly 
Membership Newsletter!<br>
<li>Huge Discounts on all MRC Books, publications, and 
merchandise - up to 50% off and sometimes more!!<br>
<li><b>FREE!!!</b> The Media Combat Kit, including MRC Reports 
on the media, bumper sticker and magnet, and samples 
of MRC Publications documenting liberal bias!<br>
<li>A monthly report from <a href="/mrc/about/bozelbio.html">L. Brent Bozell, MRC Chairman</a>
detailing what the MRC is doing to expose the leftist media!<br>
<li>Access to WEEKLY ONLINE UPDATES from the MRC!<br>
<li>Special Studies documenting liberal bias from MRC's 
Team of Researchers!<br>
<li><b>IMPACT!!!</b> Most importantly your support will enable 
us to fight the left-wing bias in the media, and expose 
their lies and distortions!<br><p>
