HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 19:49:26 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 18-Sep-96 14:24:12 GMT
Content-length: 4785
Content-type: text/html
