http://www.empower.org:80/savers/library/tabgdp.html 204.71.237.79 19970209201053 text/html 3300
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 20:11:42 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 07-Mar-96 17:47:32 GMT
