http://www.empower.org:80/savers/legislation/hr538.html 204.71.237.79 19970209201334 text/html 10664
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 20:14:20 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 28-Feb-96 15:06:17 GMT
