http://www.empower.org:80/savers/legislation/hr1042.html 204.71.237.79 19970209201501 text/html 10076
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 20:15:46 GMT
