<DOCHDR>
http://www.empower.org:80/savers/legislation/hr1780.html 204.71.237.79 19970209201543 text/html 8512
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 20:16:29 GMT
Last-modified: Wednesday, 28-Feb-96 15:06:15 GMT
Content-length: 8326
