http://www.empower.org:80/savers/legislation/hr2083.html 204.71.237.79 19970209201624 text/html 7127
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 20:17:10 GMT
