http://www.empower.org:80/savers/legislation/s722.html 204.71.237.79 19970209201717 text/html 146033
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 20:17:57 GMT
