<html>
<head>
<title>Small Business Briefing Index</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<center>
<h2> Small Business Briefing</h2>
<i>American City Business Journals</i>
<P>
SBSF President Karen Kerrigan's column appears bi-monthly
<p>

<hr>
</center>
<p><br>

<ul>
